  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist the main game now:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Enter the Arena and prove yourself worthy of being called a herald!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/1256d3e0b005cd221b8e0af67a90a519.poster.avif?t=1636733231\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/1256d3e0b005cd221b8e0af67a90a519.webm?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/1256d3e0b005cd221b8e0af67a90a519.mp4?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Be a space gladiator</strong>: combine ranged and melee weapons and choose your tactics carefully as you tailor your fighting style;<br></li><li><strong>Compete for the amusement of the crowd</strong>: overcome increasingly stronger waves of arena combatants to earn the title of a champion;<br></li><li><strong>Earn coins and trade</strong>: cunning merchants will gladly exchange your bloody rewards for powerful gear;<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/30e52e2392c259a7e5b5aeb2b935444b.webp?t=1636733231\" width=46 height=46 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Play as an ancient entity</strong>: Marduk is now available! Dismantle your foes by landing long-range shots without letting them get close.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/0a0bd1d5ec0fceca3ec9f9a29d455aaa.poster.avif?t=1636733231\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/0a0bd1d5ec0fceca3ec9f9a29d455aaa.webm?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/0a0bd1d5ec0fceca3ec9f9a29d455aaa.mp4?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/f35cd8dfb0bf9e9e4403ad5ec5a5bde4.poster.avif?t=1636733231\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/f35cd8dfb0bf9e9e4403ad5ec5a5bde4.webm?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/f35cd8dfb0bf9e9e4403ad5ec5a5bde4.mp4?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2>You come to your senses in an unknown dimension only to be offered participation in an amusement in a nearby arena. Why are you here? Who is the mastermind behind these gruesome, violent games? And most of all—<strong>can you survive?</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/361b7f38fd493246915a65b43c126bad.poster.avif?t=1636733231\" width=600 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1276730/extras/361b7f38fd493246915a65b43c126bad.webm?t=1636733231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GORGEOUS ART STYLE</h2>Jaw-dropping pixel art and hand-crafted animations will immerse you into a fantastic science fiction world full of bizarre inhabitants and extraordinary (and often extremely dangerous) creatures.",
